直至2016年1月，瓦迪的身價從210萬鎊上升到1880萬鎊，<ref name="Leicester City: Why we are all rooting for the Foxes">{{cite|title = Leicester City: Why we are all rooting for the Foxes|url = http://www.bbc.com/sport/football/35480812|publisher = BBC Sport|date = 3 Feb 2016|accessdate = 7 Feb 2016|archive-date = 2016-02-07|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160207055036/http://www.bbc.com/sport/football/35480812|dead-url = no}}</ref>領隊[[克劳迪奥·拉涅利|克劳迪奥·拉涅利]]表示他是「非賣品」。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|title=Jamie Vardy and Riyad Mahrez priceless - Claudio Ranieri|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/35098801|accessdate=17 January 2016|publisher=BBC Sport|date=7 Feb 2016|archive-date=2015-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151225223218/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/35098801|dead-url=no}}</ref> 在2月2日，他在2:0擊敗利物浦的比賽中梅開二度，第一個遠距離窩利進球被對方領隊[[尤尔根·克洛普|尤尔根·克洛普]]形容為「世界級」。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|last1=Surlis|first1=Patrick|title=Jurgen Klopp pays tribute to Leicester and Jamie Vardy after Liverpool defeat|url=http://www.skysports.com/football/news/11669/10153952/jurgen-klopp-pays-tribute-to-leicester-and-jamie-vardy-after-liverpool-defeat|accessdate=7 February 2016|publisher=Sky Sports|date=3 February 2016|archive-date=2020-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200114065435/https://www.skysports.com/football/news/11669/10153952/jurgen-klopp-pays-tribute-to-leicester-and-jamie-vardy-after-liverpool-defeat|dead-url=no}}</ref>4天之後，他與莱斯特城簽下新合約直至2019年，他的週薪也上升到80000鎊。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|title=Jamie Vardy signs new Leicester City contract until 2019|url=http://www.skysports.com/football/news/11712/10158717/jamie-vardy-signs-new-leicester-city-contract-until-2019|accessdate=7 February 2016|publisher=Sky Sports|date=7 February 2016|archive-date=2020-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200113073649/https://www.skysports.com/football/news/11712/10158717/jamie-vardy-signs-new-leicester-city-contract-until-2019|dead-url=no}}</ref>在2016年4月10日，瓦迪在李斯特2:0擊敗[[桑德兰足球俱乐部|新特蘭]]的比賽中梅開二度(他本賽的第20和第21個進球)，成為自[[加里·莱因克尔|加里·莱因克尔]]在1984-85賽季在英格蘭頂級聯賽單賽季射入20球以來首位達成此項成就的球員。賽果也導致李斯特隊史上首次晉身[[歐洲冠軍聯賽|歐洲冠軍聯賽]]資格賽並鎖定前4排名。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/35953062|title=Sunderland 0-2 Leicester|publisher=BBC Sport|date=10 April 2016|accessdate=2016-04-11|archive-date=2016-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160415034945/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/35953062|dead-url=no}}</ref>一週之後，華迪在俱樂部主場2:2逼和[[西漢姆聯足球俱樂部|西漢姆聯足球俱樂部]]的賽事中打進賽事中的首個進球，但隨後因為被球證認為他在禁區與[[安杰洛·奥邦纳|安杰洛·奥邦纳]]的碰撞是[[插水_(足球術語)|假摔]]而被兩黃一紅驅逐離場。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|last1=James|first1=Stuart|title=Jamie Vardy could face extended suspension after red card|url=http://www.irishtimes.com/sport/soccer/english-soccer/jamie-vardy-could-face-extended-suspension-after-red-card-1.2614067|accessdate=17 April 2016|work=Irish Times|date=17 April 2016|archive-date=2017-09-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170909100844/http://www.irishtimes.com/sport/soccer/english-soccer/jamie-vardy-could-face-extended-suspension-after-red-card-1.2614067|dead-url=no}}</ref>他因在場上行為不儉，在隨後被英足總紀律聆訊被罰停賽兩場並被罰款10,000鎊。並在李斯特最終的爭標奪冠成功中重要的兩場比賽中缺陣。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|last1=James|first1=Stuart|title=Leicester City's Jamie Vardy given extra game's ban for improper conduct|url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/2016/apr/25/leicester-city-jamie-vardy-one-game-ban-improper-conduct|accessdate=6 May 2016|work=The Guardian|date=26 April 2016|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108115111/http://www.theguardian.com/football/2016/apr/25/leicester-city-jamie-vardy-one-game-ban-improper-conduct|dead-url=no}}</ref>

瓦迪最終以24個入球，與[[阿古路|阿古路]]並列獲得當季英超銀靴，僅比金靴得主[[哈里·凱恩|凱恩]]少一球<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.premierleague.com/en-gb/news/news/2015-16/may/180516-harry-kane-wins-barclays-golden-boot.html|title=Kane's delight at winning Barclays Golden Boot|publisher=premierleague.com|date=18 May 2016|accessdate=19 May 2016|archive-date=2016-06-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160616192906/http://www.premierleague.com/en-gb/news/news/2015-16/may/180516-harry-kane-wins-barclays-golden-boot.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，他也成為四名入選[[PFA年度最佳陣容|PFA年度最佳陣容]]的李斯特城球員之一<ref name=PFA>{{en}}{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/36106596|accessdate=21 April 2016|title=PFA awards: Leicester and Spurs dominate Premier League team|publisher=BBC Sport|date=21 April 2016|archive-date=2016-10-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161005092158/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/36106596|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並榮獲[[英格蘭足球先生|英格蘭足球先生]]<ref name=FWA>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.skysports.com/football/news/11712/10266701/leicester-striker-jamie-vardy-named-football-writers-association-footballer-of-the-year-2015-16|title=Jamie Vardy named Football Writers' Association Footballer of the Year 2015/16|publisher=SkySports|date=2 May 2016|accessdate=2 May 2016|archive-date=2020-09-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200918140241/https://www.skysports.com/football/news/11712/10266701/leicester-striker-jamie-vardy-named-football-writers-association-footballer-of-the-year-2015-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>及[[英超最佳球員|英超最佳球員]]<ref name="Barclays Player of the Season">{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.premierleague.com/en-gb/news/news/2015-16/may/130516-leicester-city-jamie-vardy-wins-barclays-player-of-the-season.html|title=Vardy wins Barclays Player of the Season award|publisher=premierleague.com|date=13 May 2016|accessdate=19 May 2016|archive-date=2016-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160610015728/http://www.premierleague.com/en-gb/news/news/2015-16/may/130516-leicester-city-jamie-vardy-wins-barclays-player-of-the-season.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

====2016–17賽季====
2016年6月3日， [[阿仙奴|阿仙奴]]啟動了二千二百萬鎊的解約條款希望收購華迪，令李斯特城提高他的薪酬待遇 。最終，華迪認為阿仙奴不能保證他能在自己合適的位置當上正選，以及兩間阿仙奴及李斯特城兩球會戰術不同為由，拒絕了阿仙奴所提供的合約。最終華迪在6月20日他同意李斯特城為他提供的一份4年的新合同，並在[[2016年歐洲國家盃|2016年歐洲國家盃]]結束後簽署。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Reynolds|first1=Ben|title=Jamie Vardy snubbed Arsenal over reservations of role under Arsene Wenger - Sky sources|url=http://www.skysports.com/football/news/11712/10323500/jamie-vardy-snubbed-arsenal-over-reservations-of-role-under-arsene-wenger-sky-sources|accessdate=25 June 2016|publisher=Sky Sports|date=24 June 2016|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108110728/https://www.skysports.com/football/news/11712/10323500/jamie-vardy-snubbed-arsenal-over-reservations-of-role-under-arsene-wenger-sky-sources|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2016年8月7日，華迪在[[2016年慈善盾|2016年慈善盾]]中對[[曼聯|曼聯]]的比賽攻入一球，但球隊仍以1-2落敗。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/36934956|title=Community Shield: Leicester City 1-2 Manchester United|website=bbc.co.uk|publisher=BBC Sport|last=Bevan|first=Chris|date=7 August 2016|access-date=7 August 2016|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108112812/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/36934956|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2016年12月10日，華迪在對[[曼彻斯特城足球俱乐部|曼城]]的聯賽中攻入三球，替球隊以4-2擊敗對手，不但終止他連續十場比賽的入球荒，亦取得他個人首場連中三元的英超比賽。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/football/38193109 |title=Leicester City 4-2 Manchester City |date=10 December 2016 |publisher=BBC Sports |accessdate=2016-12-12 |archive-date=2016-12-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161230024212/http://www.bbc.com/sport/football/38193109 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==== 2019-20赛季 ====
2020年7月4日，瓦尔迪在与[[水晶宫足球俱乐部|水晶宫]]的比赛中梅开二度，打进了自己的第100和101个英超进球<ref>{{Cite web|title=瓦刀出鞘，山呼海啸。瓦尔迪迎来他的英超联赛100...|url=https://www.dongqiudi.com/news/1433478.html|accessdate=2020-07-04|work=www.dongqiudi.com|archive-date=2020-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200704164416/https://www.dongqiudi.com/news/1433478.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2019-2020赛季英超聯赛中，瓦尔迪打进23球，获得此赛季[[英格蘭超級足球聯賽金靴獎|金靴奖]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.skysports.com/football/news/11712/12036097/leicesters-jamie-vardy-wins-premier-league-golden-boot|title=Leicester's Jamie Vardy wins Premier League Golden Boot|website=skysports|date=26 July 2020|accessdate=26 July 2020|archive-date=2021-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210304033209/https://www.skysports.com/football/news/11712/12036097/leicesters-jamie-vardy-wins-premier-league-golden-boot|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他也打破[[迪迪埃·德罗巴|德羅巴]]（2009-10賽季）的紀錄成为了至今为止获得英超金靴奖时年龄最大的球员（33岁198天）<ref>{{cite web|url=https://sportstar.thehindu.com/football/jamie-vardy-wins-premier-league-golden-boot-leicester-city-manchester-united-danny-ings-aubameyang-salah/article32191987.ece|title=Jamie Vardy becomes oldest Premier League golden boot winner|website=sportstar|date=26 July 2020|accessdate=26 July 2020|archive-date=2020-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116194837/https://sportstar.thehindu.com/football/jamie-vardy-wins-premier-league-golden-boot-leicester-city-manchester-united-danny-ings-aubameyang-salah/article32191987.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==== 2020-21赛季 ====
