==國家隊生涯==
2015年5月21日，瓦迪首次被[[英格蘭國家足球隊|英格蘭國家隊]]徵召到和[[愛爾蘭國家足球隊|愛爾蘭]]的友誼賽以及對陣[[斯洛文尼亞國家足球隊|斯洛維尼亞]]的[[2016年歐洲國家盃外圍賽|2016年歐洲國家盃外圍賽]]。 他在同年6月7日在[[都柏林|都柏林]]的[[英華球場|英華球場]]0:0悶和愛爾蘭的賽事中完成在三獅軍團的首秀，在最後15分鐘以替補身份入替隊長[[韦恩·鲁尼|鲁尼]]。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|title=R. of Ireland 0–0 England|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/32949838|accessdate=7 June 2015|work=BBC Sport|date=7 June 2015|archive-date=2016-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160101001948/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/32949838|dead-url=no}}</ref> 同年8月30日，瓦迪再次被英格蘭徵召到對陣[[聖馬力諾國家足球隊|聖馬力諾]]和[[瑞士國家足球隊|瑞士]]兩場2016年歐洲國家盃外圍賽的球員名單，<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|title=Internationals: England's Vardy Among LCFC Contingent|url=http://www.lcfc.com/news/article/internationals-englands-vardy-among-lcfc-contingent-2658100.aspx|accessdate=30 August 2015|work=Leicester City F.C.|date=30 August 2015|archive-date=2017-05-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170528155410/http://www.lcfc.com//news/article/internationals-englands-vardy-among-lcfc-contingent-2658100.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref> 6天之後，他在[[塞拉瓦莱|塞拉瓦莱]]6:0大勝前者的比賽中首發上陣。<ref>{{en}}{{Cite news|url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/34165282|title=San Marino v England: How the players rated|date=5 September 2015|work=British Broadcasting Corporation|accessdate=2016-02-06|archive-date=2015-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151225022937/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/34165282|dead-url=no}}</ref>瓦迪在2016年3月26日3:2擊敗[[德國國家足球隊|德國]]的比賽中取得首個國際賽進球，他以後備身份上陣並接應[[纳塔涅尔·克莱因|纳塔涅尔·克莱因]]的傳球用後腳破網協助英格蘭2:2追平對手。<ref name="Germany 2–3 England"/> 3天之後他再次取得入球，在[[溫布萊球場|溫布萊球場]]2:1擊敗[[荷蘭國家足球隊|荷蘭]]的熱身賽中他打進賽事中的第一球。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/2016/mar/29/england-holland-international-friendly-match-report|title=England frustrated as Luciano Narsingh goal seals Holland's comeback|date=29 March 2016|work=Guardian|accessdate=30 March 2016|archive-date=2019-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190713142501/https://www.theguardian.com/football/2016/mar/29/england-holland-international-friendly-match-report|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在6月15日，在2016歐洲杯英格蘭對陣威爾士的小組賽中上半場踢完以0:1落後，他和[[丹尼爾·史杜歷治|斯圖里奇]]下半場開始時上場替換[[哈里·凱恩|凱恩]]和[[拉謙·史達寧|斯特林]]後分別打進追平分和超前分，助隊伍以2:1逆轉晉級16強。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/football/2016/06/16/england-2-wales-1-daniel-sturridge-and-jamie-vardy-come-off-the/|title=England 2 Wales 1: Daniel Sturridge and Jamie Vardy come off the bench to secure last-gasp win|publisher=The Telegraph|author1=Jason Burt|date=16 June 2016|accessdate=16 June 2016|archive-date=2020-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201122204959/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/football/2016/06/16/england-2-wales-1-daniel-sturridge-and-jamie-vardy-come-off-the/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 在本次賽事中，有媒體報導指稱他和隊長魯尼有爭執，但被教練[[罗伊·霍奇森|霍奇森]]否認。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|last1=Crellin|first1=Mark|title=Wayne Rooney and Jamie Vardy are close friends, says Roy Hodgson|url=http://www.skysports.com/football/news/12016/10325817/wayne-rooney-and-jamie-vardy-are-close-friends-says-roy-hodgson|accessdate=28 June 2016|publisher=Sky Sports|date=27 June 2016|archive-date=2020-06-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200616213305/https://www.skysports.com/football/news/12016/10325817/wayne-rooney-and-jamie-vardy-are-close-friends-says-roy-hodgson|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2018年世界杯時他再次入選23人名單。雖然本次大賽中英格蘭久違的重返四強，但基本上教練團最屬意的前場組合還是凱恩和斯特林的搭配，瓦迪只能替補出賽，也沒有太多表現機會。賽後，他跟總教練[[盖雷斯·索斯盖特|索斯盖特]]表示，除非有嚴重傷病導致缺人，不然他不會再配合徵招。

==踢球風格==
{{Quote box |width=25% |align=right |quoted=1 |quote=他有很高的力量和專注力。他有一份強大的心智和永不放棄的態度。他的風格可以鼓舞隊友，使他們跟著奮戰。|salign=right |source=— [[克劳迪奥·拉涅利|克劳迪奥·拉涅利]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.express.co.uk/sport/football/614268/Leicester-boss-Claudio-Ranieri-Jamie-Vardy-Premier-League-Crystal-Palace-match-preview |title=Leicester boss heaps praise on Jamie Vardy after battling back from broken wrist |date=24 October 2015 |accessdate=29 November 2015 |work=Sunday Express |archive-date=2020-08-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809101501/https://www.express.co.uk/sport/football/614268/Leicester-boss-Claudio-Ranieri-Jamie-Vardy-Premier-League-Crystal-Palace-match-preview |dead-url=no }}</ref>}}
與瓦迪同樣從業餘聯賽出道到英超和國家隊的著名球星[[伊恩·胡禮|伊恩·萊特]]在2015年10月表示瓦迪將會成為英格蘭在[[2016年歐洲足球錦標賽|2016年歐洲足球錦標賽]]的[[薩爾瓦托雷·斯基拉奇|薩爾瓦托雷·斯基拉奇]]：「斯基拉奇，另一個大器晚成的球員，在[[1990年世界盃足球賽|1990年世界盃足球賽]]開始前只是一個眾多球星背後的替補球員，在最終成為最佳射手。」<ref name=wright>{{cite news|last1=Wright|first1=Ian|title=Jamie Vardy can be England's Toto Schillaci at Euro 2016|url=h。ttp://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/34611895|accessdate=25 October 2015|publisher=BBC Sport|date=23 October 2015|archive-date=2015-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151025211433/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/34611895|dead-url=no}}</ref> 萊特在效力[[伯恩利足球俱樂部|伯恩利]]期間的前隊友[[米奇·梅隆|米奇·梅隆]]為費列伍德將瓦迪簽下，也是一位了解瓦迪的教練。認為瓦迪是一個在第一時間觸球時良好而又勤奮的球員，為防守者製造不斷的麻煩，本能地發揮自己的能力而不是由教練去培訓出來。<ref name=wright/>

隨着他的進球數日益增加，瓦迪為人所知的是他的高工作效率，不斷地跑動以及直接的進攻方法;<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/football/2015/may/21/leicester-jamie-vardy-england|title=Leicester’s Jamie Vardy scales new heights with England call-up|date=21 May 2015|work=The Guardian|accessdate=26 October 2015|archive-date=2020-06-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200616221450/https://www.theguardian.com/football/2015/may/21/leicester-jamie-vardy-england|dead-url=no}}</ref> 他也是一名異常高速和動態前鋒，也是一名有一定制空力以及也用雙腳射門的球員。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.skysports.com/football/news/30385/10037779/jamie-vardy-is-the-premier-league-top-scorer-can-he-keep-it-up|title=Jamie Vardy is the Premier League top scorer: Can he keep it up?|publisher=Sky Sports|author1=Adam Bate|date=22 October 2015|accessdate=25 October 2015|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108095747/http://www.skysports.com/football/news/30385/10037779/jamie-vardy-is-the-premier-league-top-scorer-can-he-keep-it-up|dead-url=no}}</ref> [[英格蘭國家足球隊|英格蘭]]教練團成員和[[天空體育台|天空體育台]]權威人士[[加利·尼維利|蓋瑞·奈維爾]]評論了瓦迪的踢球風格如何影響隊友:「他為球隊的休息設置了節奏和頻率，讓其他球員在他背後沒有任何不努力的藉口。」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.express.co.uk/sport/football/614359/Manchester-United-Gary-Neville-hails-Jamie-Vardy-England-great|title=Manchester United legend hails Jamie Vardy as one of the great England forwards|publisher=Daily Express|author1=Colin Mafham|date=25 October 2015|accessdate=31 October 2015|archive-date=2020-06-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200616204809/https://www.express.co.uk/sport/football/614359/Manchester-United-Gary-Neville-hails-Jamie-Vardy-England-great|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==個人生活==
瓦迪的父親是一名裝修工人-Richard Gill而母親為女學生Lisa Clewes。他父親在隨後跟另一女人遠走高飛後，他的母親改嫁予Philip Vardy。Gill在2015年11月被「[[週日郵報|週日郵報]]」查獲，他對報館承認，他並不知道他的兒子成為一名職業足球運動員。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Joseph|first1=Claudia|title=Football's record-breaker is my son? You're KIDDING! Astonishing moment the MoS tells labourer he is the long-lost father of goal-scoring sensation Jamie Vardy (and he'd never even heard of him)|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3347619/Football-s-record-breaker-son-KIDDING-Astonishing-moment-MoS-tells-labourer-long-lost-father-goal-scoring-sensation-Jamie-Vardy-d-never-heard-him.html|date=5 December 2015|accessdate=6 December 2015|work=Daily Mail|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305054347/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3347619/Football-s-record-breaker-son-KIDDING-Astonishing-moment-MoS-tells-labourer-long-lost-father-goal-scoring-sensation-Jamie-Vardy-d-never-heard-him.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在成為職業球員之前，瓦迪在業餘球員時期曾經是一名製造醫療[[夾板|夾板]]的技工。<ref>{{citation|title=Our Jamie has come so Var|first=Stuart|last=Hammond|work=The Non-League Paper|page=7|date=28 September 2014}}</ref>在2007年，他因為酒吧外毆打的事件而得到定罪，並安裝了六個月電子監察裝置，而他的宵禁令也限制了他在史托斯橋鋼鐵的上場時間。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Brooks|first1=Gideon|title=Exclusive: Jamie Vardy's former chairman reveals how assault conviction changed career|url=http://www.express.co.uk/sport/football/622586/Jamie-Vardy-Leicester-assault-conviction-Premier-League|accessdate=29 November 2015|work=Daily Express|date=28 November 2015|archive-date=2020-11-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201123170633/https://www.express.co.uk/sport/football/622586/Jamie-Vardy-Leicester-assault-conviction-Premier-League|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2015年8月，「週日太陽報」發放一段瓦迪上個月在賭場的影片，他在片中稱一名東亞男人為"[[Jap|Jap]]"。他隨後以「令人遺憾的錯誤判斷」的方式道歉，繼而被莱斯特城把他帶到一個教育課程作懲罰。<ref>{{cite news|title=Leicester City fine Jamie Vardy over racist incident|url=http://www.rte.ie/sport/soccer/2015/0813/721096-leicester-fine-jamie-vardy-over-racist/|accessdate=2 September 2015|publisher=RTÉ|date=13 August 2015|archive-date=2020-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200926023122/https://www.rte.ie/sport/soccer/2015/0813/721096-leicester-fine-jamie-vardy-over-racist/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2015年11月，瓦迪推出V9學院計劃，每年為期一週的訓練營旨在提供輔導和指導60個非聯賽的球員，並為他們提供機會從聯賽俱樂部的球探面前展示自己的才華。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/34950055|title=Jamie Vardy: Leicester striker launches non-league academy|date=27 November 2015|work=British Broadcasting Corporation|accessdate=2016-03-05|archive-date=2015-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151130065909/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/34950055|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.theguardian.com/football/2015/nov/27/jamie-vardy-leicester-academy-non-league|title=Leicester’s Jamie Vardy sets up academy to help non-league talent|date=27 November 2015|work=The Guardian|accessdate=2016-03-05|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108185704/http://www.theguardian.com/football/2015/nov/27/jamie-vardy-leicester-academy-non-league|dead-url=no}}</ref> 同一個月，史托斯橋鋼鐵將他們的主看台命為瓦迪看台。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Bernstein|first1=Joe|title=Jamie Vardy's first club Stocksbridge Park Steels to name main stand after Leicester's record-breaking goal-scorer|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-3337989/Jamie-Vardy-s-club-Stocksbridge-Park-Steels-main-stand-Leicester-s-record-breaking-goal-scorer.html|accessdate=29 November 2015|work=Daily Mail|date=29 November 2015|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304104212/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-3337989/Jamie-Vardy-s-club-Stocksbridge-Park-Steels-main-stand-Leicester-s-record-breaking-goal-scorer.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>在2015年12月-[[萊斯特|萊斯特]]食品生產商[[步行者（休閒食品）|步行者]]帶出了限量版「Vardy咸」[[馬鈴薯片|馬鈴薯片]]味，以表彰瓦迪的不斷的進球。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Gibson|first1=Sean|title=Jamie Vardy gets his own limited edition Walkers crisp flavour|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/teams/leicester-city/12046867/Jamie-Vardy-gets-his-own-limited-edition-Walkers-crisp-flavour.html|accessdate=12 December 2015|work=The Telegraph|date=11 December 2015|archive-date=2020-06-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200616215737/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/teams/leicester-city/12046867/Jamie-Vardy-gets-his-own-limited-edition-Walkers-crisp-flavour.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

